Revision history for Dist::Zilla::Plugin::LoadTests

{{$NEXT}}

0.06    2010.11.07
	- Added a "SEE ALSO" section to the more generic but slower [CompileTests]
          (AZAWAWI)

0.05    2010.10.28
	- Reverted to the simpler method of skipping the load test when
	  $ENV{DISPLAY} is not set on non-win32 platforms (AZAWAWI)
	- Removed Test::NeedsDisplay dependency (AZAWAWI)

0.04    2010.10.28
	- Added forgotten Test::NeedsDisplay test dependency (AZAWAWI)

0.03    2010.10.27
	- The 'name' option is used instead of the 'module' option (AZAWAWI)

0.02    2010.10.26
	- It works now as expected (AZAWAWI)
	- Renamed 'module_name' option to 'module' (AZAWAWI)
	- Added the 'needs_display' option uses Test::NeedsDisplay
	  ':skip_all' if enabled (AZAWAWI)

0.01    2010.10.26
	First version, released on an unsuspecting world. (AZAWAWI)
